-
TKINTER BASIC WIDGET

label - Display a text
Button - Triggers a function
Entry - Allows user text input
Frame - Groups widgets for better layout and spacing

EXAMPLE#1
import tkinter as TK

windows_ko = TK.Tk()
windows_ko.title("OOP LA28")
windows_ko.geometry("300x200")
windows_ko.configure(bg="white")

frame = TK.Frame(windows_ko)
frame.pack(pady=20)

label = TK.Label(frame, text="This is Label")
label.grid(row=0, column=0, padx=10, pady=10 )

windows_ko.mainloop()


